  "texts": [
    "For S. lycopersicum a true positive rate (TPR) of 0.9 and a true negative rate of 0.72 (TNR) indicated higher confidence for the positive predictions.",
    "This reflected the distribution of the expression predictions for genes of the \"middle\" second and third quartiles (Fig. 6a; yellow distributions).",
    "The same was observed for S. pennellii, with a TPR of 0.86 and a TNR of 0.81 (Fig. 6b).",
    "To estimate if these MSR predictions are indicative of physiological and metabolic differences between the two species, we performed Mercator4 MapMan annotation of functional gene ontology on the S. lycopersicum and S. pennellii proteome 38.",
    "Then, we expressed each functional category in terms of the observed (true labels) and predicted expression (prediction probabilities) of genes classified into each functional category."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
